---
layout: layouts/base.njk
brand: devbyhwang
title: 소개
description: "DevByHwang 소개"
---
<article class="about-page">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>DevByHwang</h1>
  </header>

  <section class="about-content about-profile">
    <img class="profile-img profile-img-large" src="{{ '/assets/profile.png' | url }}" alt="Hwang 프로필 사진" width="120" height="120" loading="lazy" />
    <p>서비스를 만들고, 작은 실험을 공개하고, 그 과정을 기록합니다.</p>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="{{ '/devbyhwang/playground/' | url }}">Playground</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/devbyhwang/blog/' | url }}">글 아카이브</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/devbyhwang/categories/games/' | url }}">게임 카테고리</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/devbyhwang/categories/freelance/' | url }}">외주 카테고리</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="about-contact-block">
      <div class="about-contact-email-row">
        {% if site.email %}<a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>{% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="profile-links about-contact-social-row">
        {% if site.socials.github %}<a href="{{ site.socials.github }}">GitHub</a>{% endif %}
        {% if site.socials.kmong %}<a href="{{ site.socials.kmong }}">Kmong</a>{% endif %}
        {% if site.socials.youtube %}<a href="{{ site.socials.youtube }}">YouTube</a>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</article>
